0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5774,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/31\/prophet-dawah-world-leaders\/","url_meta":{"origin":2766,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Da&#8217;wah: The Prophet invites world leaders to Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: Before the passing away of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, he had written to Khosrau, to Casear, to Negus, and to every tyrant, inviting them to Allah. This was not the same Negus for whom the Prophet had performed the funeral\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33192,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/14\/muslims-rejoice-victory-christians\/","url_meta":{"origin":2766,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Romans: Muslims rejoice at victory of Christians over idolaters","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id reported: On the day of the battle of Badr, the Romans were victorious over the Persians and the believers were pleased by that. Allah had revealed, \u201cThe Romans were defeated in the nearest land, but they will be victorious after their defeat in a few years. To Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40382,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/06\/05\/umar-faris-rum\/","url_meta":{"origin":2766,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Wealth: Umar asks for the riches of Persia and Rome","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, call upon Allah to send abundance upon your nation, for the Persians and Romans enjoy abundance and have been given the world, yet they do not worship Allah as they recline on their couches!\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20557,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/04\/10\/what-if-dunya-given-to-you\/","url_meta":{"origin":2766,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Fitnah: What if the world is given to you?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 10, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf the treasures of Persia and Rome were opened for you, what kind of people will you be?\u201d Abdur Rahman ibn Awf said, \u201cWe will be as Allah has ordered us.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cPerhaps\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\